---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About - Paper to PowerPoint Flowchart Generator">
  <main>
    <section class="about-section">
      <h1>About Our Project</h1>
      
      <div class="about-content">
        <h2>What We Do</h2>
        <p>
          Our Paper to PowerPoint Flowchart Generator is an AI-powered tool that automatically converts academic papers and text into structured PowerPoint presentations with flowcharts. We aim to save researchers, students, and professionals valuable time by automating the process of visualizing complex information.
        </p>
        
        <h2>How It Works</h2>
        <p>
          Our system uses advanced AI models to analyze the content of research papers or text inputs. It identifies the main processes, methodologies, or frameworks described in the paper and generates a Mermaid flowchart representation. This flowchart is then enhanced with appropriate emojis and converted into a PowerPoint presentation that you can download and use.
        </p>
        
        <h2>Technology Stack</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Frontend:</strong> Astro, React</li>
          <li><strong>AI Processing:</strong> OpenRouter API with Gemini model</li>
          <li><strong>Flowchart Generation:</strong> Mermaid.js</li>
          <li><strong>PowerPoint Generation:</strong> pptxgenjs</li>
          <li><strong>PDF Processing:</strong> pdf-parse</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2>Future Enhancements</h2>
        <p>
          We're continuously working to improve our system. Future enhancements may include:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Support for more complex diagram types</li>
          <li>Enhanced customization options</li>
          <li>Integration with reference management systems</li>
          <li>Collaborative editing features</li>
          <li>More presentation templates and styles</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  main {
    margin: auto;
    padding: 1rem;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 1000px;
    color: #333;
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  
  .about-section {
    background-color: white;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
    padding: 2rem;
    margin: 2rem 0;
  }
  
  h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    color: #1f2937;
    text-align: center;
  }
  
  h2 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: #1f2937;
    border-bottom: 2px solid #e5e7eb;
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  
  p {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  
  ul {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }
  
  li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  
  .about-content {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
</style>
